# Keep the Vercel upload lean. Vercel installs dependencies and builds from
# source using the buildCommand in vercel.json, so local build artifacts and
# the Python pipeline are not needed in the deployment. Paths are anchored with
# a leading slash so app/src/data (which the app imports) is not excluded.
node_modules
/app/node_modules
/app/dist
/.git
/pipeline
/data
/archive
/docs
__pycache__
*.pyc
